s Card 都叫好嘅, 好多時7-11 OK 買iTunes Card 有折...."},{"pid":"45368ccefc0b170ad2c80df268e0e5fb40fb14e1","tid":51080,"uid":12820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>退出family<br />\n本身佢咁設定應該就係為咗防造假家庭<br />\n就算如果真嘅成年家庭用都會好煩，個個用同一張卡畀錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一退出family  apple music啲歌又會無晒要重新down過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394ad4d1cb09d165ae915ce460448650697a4ca2","tid":51080,"uid":4284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唯一方法係用iTunes card 入錢, 咁就會先扣咗itunes card啲錢先扣你frd 信用卡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nitunes pass 都係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0b4abfdf74723f854871249dc3009e41c18340","tid":51080,"uid":12820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唯一方法係用iTunes card 入錢, 咁就會先扣咗itunes card啲錢先扣你frd 信用卡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢招都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有用開Apple Music 買iTunes Card 都叫好嘅, 好多時7-11 OK 買iTunes Card 有折....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果買iCloud 容量的話 都係會先扣iTunes card先?"},{"pid":"ff9f983b3056a9033c95b39e5742b9a085b34220","tid":51080,"uid":12820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"再問埋 如果我退出咗family<br />\n再買iCloud 入返family畀錢嗰到會唔會即刻彈返去我朋友張卡到?<br />\n唔該晒答我問題嘅巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b07668fa5f0a25da9ebce92ad68d69299dbb1d9","tid":51080,"uid":12399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢招都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有用開Apple Music 買iTunes Card 都叫好嘅, 好多時7-11 OK 買iTunes Card 有折....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果買iCloud 容量的話 都係會先扣iTunes card先?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔理你係咪family member, 所有個人purchase 都會優先扣itunes card balance(如有), 多餘嘅就先至扣信用卡 (你個情況因為你係family member, 所以係會扣你朋友信用卡嘅錢)<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 未試過 但google過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都join咗family, 朋友用我信用卡買嘢"},{"pid":"8379bd6f2ffe0d0a953fb9b7e16c508572a0e25f","tid":51080,"uid":12820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有用開Apple Music 買iTunes Card 都叫好嘅, 好多時7-11 OK 買iTunes Card 有折....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果買iCloud 容量的話 都係會先扣iTunes card先?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔理你係咪family member, 所有個人purchase 都會優先扣itunes card balance(如有), 多餘嘅就先至扣信用卡 (你個情況因為你係family member, 所以係會扣你朋友信用卡嘅錢)<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 未試過 但google過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都join咗family, 朋友用我信用卡買嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該唔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我下次試下先"}]}